#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bowling.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Customers are hungry? Allow them to purchase drinks, snacks and a bite "
"through the <strong>Point of Sale app</strong>"
msgstr ""
"Les clients ont faim ? Donnez-leur la possibilité d’acheter des boissons, "
"snacks et plats via l’application <strong>Point de Vente</strong>."

#. module: bowling
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bowling.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Customers can also rent bowling shoes - keep an eye on which lanes are "
"supposed to return how many shoes at a glance using the Point of Sale order "
"overviews."
msgstr ""
"Les clients peuvent également louer des chaussures de bowling – gardez un "
"aperçu clair du nombre de chaussures à retourner par piste via les vues "
"commandes du Point de Vente."

#. module: bowling
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bowling.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Customers can book a session using the <strong>Appointments app's page </"
"strong>on your website, and pay in just a few clicks"
msgstr ""
"Les clients peuvent réserver une session via <strong>la page de "
"l'application Rendez-vous</strong> sur votre site web, et payer en quelques "
"clics."

#. module: bowling
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bowling.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Customers hungry, or need to book a lane on the spot? Just use the Point of "
"Sale app to manage food sales, and attribute them to the correct bowling "
"lanes to keep an easy overview of what goes where."
msgstr ""
"Clients affamés ou besoin de réserver une piste sur place ? Utilisez "
"simplement l’application Point de Vente pour gérer les ventes de nourriture, "
"et attribuez-les aux bonnes pistes de bowling pour garder une vue d’ensemble "
"claire."

#. module: bowling
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bowling.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Customize your appointment reminders to tailor them to your company's "
"branding"
msgstr ""
"Personnalisez vos rappels de rendez-vous pour les adapter à l’identité "
"visuelle de votre entreprise."

